# HTW Constitution

This is a proposed split for review. It is not active.

This file takes precedence over subordinate files.
Read and obey the following subordinate documents in order.

1. `swarmforge/constitution-proposed/project.prompt`
2. `swarmforge/constitution-proposed/engineering.prompt`
3. `swarmforge/constitution-proposed/workflow.prompt`

If two subordinate files conflict, the earlier file wins.
